<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<!--
 Code Artifact: ic_launcher_foreground.xml
 Description: Draws the simple HUD-Link launcher foreground mark used by the adaptive icon.
 Programmer: HudLink development team (Brandon Dodge, Zach Sevart, Asa Maker, Jonathan Gott, Josh Dwoskin)
 Date Created: 2026-02-15
 Revision History:
 - 2026-02-15 - Zach Sevart - Added starter launcher artwork.
 - 2026-04-26 - HudLink development team - Added release prologue comments for sprint submission.
 Preconditions: Android resource tools compile this vector as a drawable resource.
 Acceptable Inputs: Valid vector dimensions, viewport values, fill colors, and path data.
 Unacceptable Inputs: Malformed path data, invalid colors, or dimensions that break launcher icon rendering.
 Postconditions: The adaptive icon can reference a stable foreground drawable.
 Return Values: Vector XML does not return values; Android generates drawable resource IDs.
 Error and Exception Conditions: Resource compilation fails on invalid vector XML or path data.
 Side Effects: Adds launcher artwork to the generated APK resources.
 Invariants: The foreground remains a simple H mark for HUD-Link branding.
 Known Faults: Artwork is placeholder-level and can be replaced by a final brand asset.
 Major Blocks: The vector root defines the canvas, and the path draws the foreground mark.
 Line Comments: XML comments are kept at the artifact level because vector path data is easier to read without trailing notes.
-->
<vector xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android"
    android:width="108dp"
    android:height="108dp"
    android:viewportWidth="108"
    android:viewportHeight="108">
    <!-- Simple "H" for HUD-Link -->
    <path
        android:fillColor="#FFFFFF"
        android:pathData="M38,30 L38,78 L46,78 L46,58 L62,58 L62,78 L70,78 L70,30 L62,30 L62,50 L46,50 L46,30 Z"/>
</vector>
